Wouldn't be accurate to call her
an easywoman, 'cause easy she wasn't.

323
00:30:32,972 --> 00:30:35,736
MaryAnn, that was her name.

324
00:30:35,808 --> 00:30:37,799
MaryAnn was barren...

325
