ifshe hadn't stolen all my money.

331
00:30:59,699 --> 00:31:02,827
Now, mind you, and I'm not
too embarrassed to admit it...

332
00:31:02,902 --> 00:31:06,133
mind you,
she had charged me handsomely...

333
00:31:06,205 --> 00:31:09,140
