and she's gone with everything I own.

335
00:31:13,613 --> 00:31:15,547
Can you believe that?

336
00:31:16,616 --> 00:31:19,483
- That's awful.
- What'd you say?

337
00:31:19,552 --> 00:31:23,488
I said, that's awful--
your tale ofmisfortune.

338
00:31:25,691 --> 00:31:28,125
Quite awful.

339
00:31:29,462 --> 00:31:32,397
The ''awfulest.''

340
00:31:32,465 --> 00:31:36,060
Didn't make me feel any better
to find out...

341
00:31:36,135 --> 00:31:40,071
