It reeks in here.

400
00:39:36,382 --> 00:39:38,475
That was--

401
00:39:38,550 --> 00:39:41,542
- You were quite forceful, darling.
- Sorry.

402
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:43,713
No, I like it.

403
00:39:43,789 --> 00:39:46,724
Perhaps the ocean air
is bringing out the animal in you.

404
00:39:52,531 --> 00:39:54,863
Look, Angus, we have to talk.

405
00:39:54,934 --> 00:39:58,199
You know I hate conversations
that start with, ''Look, Angus.''

406
00:39:58,270 --> 00:40:00,329
It's about me.

407
00:40:00,406 --> 00:40:03,432
Then I am interested.
As long as it's not about me.

408
00:40:03,509 --> 00:40:06,034
I'm bored to the hilt with me.

409
00:40:06,111 --> 00:40:11,981
My past is quite different
than what I've told you.

410
00:40:15,054 --> 00:40:16,988
For one, I was never
a famous actress in London.

411
00:40:17,056 --> 00:40:21,857
And I was never a champion swimmer.
In fact, I can't even swim.

412
00:40:21,927 --> 00:40:24,896
