I was running away.

413
00:40:27,199 --> 00:40:29,133
There were men.

414
00:40:31,103 --> 00:40:36,541
There were several men
with whom I became acquainted.

415
00:40:38,744 --> 00:40:40,006
You understand?

416
00:40:42,648 --> 00:40:46,584
I don't care whatyou were
orwhatyou did beforeyou met me.

417
00:40:48,153 --> 00:40:49,745
