I'm no saint meself.

419
00:41:02,935 --> 00:41:04,869
But that's not all.

420
00:41:07,373 --> 00:41:09,637
Miles was one ofthe men
I knew back in London.

421
00:41:11,143 --> 00:41:12,906
The Yankee sailor boy?

422
00:41:14,580 --> 00:41:15,945
That Miles.

423
00:41:17,516 --> 00:41:20,747
