I will straighten him out.

427
00:41:30,896 --> 00:41:32,989
- You can't.
- Oh, yes, I can.

428
00:41:33,065 --> 00:41:36,933
He may be a big fella, but he'll be
hungover. I'll have the upper hand.

429
00:41:37,002 --> 00:41:40,597
